@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix : <http://www.example.com/ontology#> .

:Customer rdf:type owl:Class .
:System rdf:type owl:Class .
:Shipment rdf:type owl:Class .
:Track rdf:type owl:Class .
:hasStatus rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .
:allowedTo rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .

:Track rdfs:subClassOf :Shipment .
:Customer rdfs:subClassOf :System .

:hasStatus rdfs:domain :Track .
:hasStatus rdfs:range xsd:string .

:allowedTo rdfs:domain :Customer .
:allowedTo rdfs:range :Track .

:System rdfs:comment "The system shall allow customers to track shipment status in real time." .
